data.description: Welcome to this charming brand-new construction, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom with additional recreation room and home office to utilize however you desire! This home is located within biking distance, just about a mile to quaint downtown Meredith. Situated in an ideal location, this property offers the perfect blend of modern living and small-town charm.  The open-concept design creates a welcoming atmosphere, with an eat-in kitchen featuring clean white cabinets and stunning granite countertops. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or enjoying a casual breakfast, this kitchen is sure to be the heart of the home.  This home is perfect for those seeking easy living. Step outside onto a beautiful outdoor pergola which provides shade and a lovely focal point for gatherings with family and friends. The possibilities are endless for outdoor enjoyment in this space. One of the standout features of this property is its proximity to the town park, adding to the appeal of this family-friendly neighborhood. For those who appreciate lake living, you'll be delighted to know that lake access is available to Meredith residents on both Lake Waukewan and the renowned Lake Winnipesaukee. Enjoy boating, swimming, and all the activities these lakes have to offer. This property also comes with a short-term rental history, providing potential income possibilities. This brand-new construction home offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in the heart of Meredith.
